WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.280 --> 00:00:08.400
There is a world, far away from the
hustle and bustle of modern cities, where

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:14.280
towns lie on the edge of jungles. The
students wear their best shoes,

00:00:14.280 --> 00:00:18.940
except for Edermira Castro. 
She wears no shoes.

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:25.220
Edermira can wear little more than beach sandals.
She was born with what Americans call

00:00:25.220 --> 00:00:31.960
club feet, but the people of Rancho
Grande called them 'pies deformados.'

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:36.840
Edermira's feet are so severely turned in
that the delicate skin on top of the

00:00:36.840 --> 00:00:42.990
foot is on the bottom. Toes that would
provide balance cannot. Her deformed

00:00:42.990 --> 00:00:47.520
feet keep Edermira from doing many
things a kid likes to do. Simple things

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:53.400
like run or ride a bicycle,
jump rope or skip. There is so much

00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:57.690
work for doctors to do on Edermira's
feet that it will require Edermira to

00:00:57.690 --> 00:01:05.100
live for eight months in America. Soon it
is surgery day. Today Edermira will

00:01:05.100 --> 00:01:09.049
have the first surgery on her feet.

00:01:09.300 --> 00:01:16.450
Thousands of miles from home, unfamiliar
surroundings, masked faces, you're scared

00:01:16.450 --> 00:01:21.700
and don't know what to expect.
The girl from Rancho Grande is only 13

00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:28.380
years old. Normally she would turn to her
mother, today she turns to Roberta.

00:01:30.140 --> 00:01:34.440
Roberta does the things she knows Edermira's mother would do.

00:01:34.440 --> 00:01:39.600
She comforts Edermira and she prays.

00:01:39.810 --> 00:01:45.149
Although Edermira may not be able to
understand, she sees it in Roberta's eyes.

00:01:45.149 --> 00:01:51.240
It is a look that says everything is
going to be alright.

00:01:55.860 --> 00:02:01.539
The biggest worry is that she comes out
of this in better shape than she came

00:02:01.539 --> 00:02:08.590
here. It's always risky. I just hope
everything is successful for her. I want

00:02:08.590 --> 00:02:15.250
to see her walking home in shoes and, you know, being able to run with other kids.

